    rdfs:label "Application Architecture@en"@en .

###  https://example.org/ont/leanix#LXO0023

leanix:LXO0023 rdf:type owl:Class ;
    rdfs:subClassOf leanix:LXO0022 , leanix:LXO0059 ;
    rdfs:comment "Technology-based product or service delivering measurable customer value. (source LeanIX)@en"@en ;
