    rdfs:label "Information Architecture@en"@en .

###  https://example.org/ont/leanix#LXO0030

leanix:LXO0030 rdf:type owl:Class ;
    rdfs:subClassOf leanix:LXO0029 , leanix:LXO0059 ;
